data.eml:eml: Genus- and family-group names in the order Embioptera (Insecta)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Miller, Kelly B. (2009): Genus- and family-group names in the order Embioptera (Insecta). Zootaxa 2055: 1-34, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.186678
